[
  {
    "text": "日々の暮らしの織物",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.09987810123318035,
      "left": 0.35296031617567253,
      "width": 0.29404398938174503,
      "height": 0.025246211069286623
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "朝の日差しが静かな通りを優し",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.15505268267341019,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "く照らし、温かな光が木々の間",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.17399207582366275,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を通り抜けて地面に美しい影を",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.19293146897391528,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "落としています。鳥たちが木の",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.21187086212416784,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.2260870360043389,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "上で優しく歌い、その心地よい",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.23081025527442037,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "さえずりが眠っていた街を目覚",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.24974964842467293,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22641373488778527,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "め",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2686890415749253,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.016335784327307982,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "させ、新しい一",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2686890415749253,
      "left": 0.13398282113306847,
      "width": 0.11435038759630724,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "日が希望と可",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2686890415749253,
      "left": 0.24833319161356765,
      "width": 0.09801462038480735,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "能性に満ちた始まりを迎えま",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.28762843472517785,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.2123649908653065,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "す。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3065678278754304,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.03103798224412815,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "技術の進歩は前例のないスピー",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3378178265733471,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22723054759884947,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ドで私たちの生活様式と働き方",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.35675721972359953,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を根本的に変えています。人工",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3756966128738521,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22576031837089325,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "知能から再生可能エネルギーま",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.39463600602410454,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "で、毎",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4135753991743571,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.048353883483416515,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "日新しい革新と発明",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4135753991743571,
      "left": 0.16600092028917707,
      "width": 0.147021922019307,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "が現",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4135753991743571,
      "left": 0.313022825192676,
      "width": 0.03267155153880782,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "れ、これらの技術的進歩は社会",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.43251479232460965,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "のあらゆる側面に深い影響を与",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4514541854748621,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "え、私たちが世界と関わる方法",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.47039357862511466,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を再構築しています。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4893329717753672,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.16074396715833938,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "古代文明は驚くべき記念碑と建",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5205829704732838,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22739388766557297,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "築の奇跡を建設し、これらの壮",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5395223636235364,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "大な構造物は何千年もの時を経",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5584617567737888,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ても堂々と立ち続けています。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5774011499240415,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.2270671887821267,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "エ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.596340543074294,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.016335784327307982,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ジプトのピラミッドから中国",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.596340543074294,
      "left": 0.13398282113306847,
      "width": 0.2123649908653065,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "の万里の長",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6152799362245465,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.08167885317330749,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "城まで、これらの建",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6152799362245465,
      "left": 0.19932588997906797,
      "width": 0.14636848675241584,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "築物は先祖の卓越した知恵と驚",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.634219329374799,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "くべき創",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6531587225250515,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.06403621555057423,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "造性を示すだけでな",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6531587225250515,
      "left": 0.18168325235633476,
      "width": 0.147021922019307,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "く、人類文明の輝かしい歴史の",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.672098115675304,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946374
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "証人でもあります。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6910375088255567,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.14538835272462727,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "教育は社会の進歩と個人の成長",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.723234477180986,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を推進する根本的な基礎です。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7421738703312385,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.2270671887821267,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "体系的な学習と継続的な知識の",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7611132634814911,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "蓄積を通じて、人々は自分たち",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7800526566317435,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22804732280991524,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "の生活と周囲のコ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7980450801244834,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.1306861548078071,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ミュニティを",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7980450801244834,
      "left": 0.24833319161356765,
      "width": 0.09752454393463894,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "改善するために必要な様々な道",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8169844732747359,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.22870075807680643,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "具、技能、そして深い洞察を獲",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8359238664249884,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.2277206052990186,
      "height": 0.012623105439946356
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "得し、より良い未来の構築に貢",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.15505268267341019,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.228700758076806,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "献することができます。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.17399207582366275,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.17805988714762674,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "自",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2052420745215794,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.01633578432730796,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "然は比類のない美しい景観と",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2052420745215794,
      "left": 0.4019630550652642,
      "width": 0.21236499086530614,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "生命を維持するために不可欠な",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.22418146767183195,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.228700758076806,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "貴重な資源を惜しみなく提供し",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.24312086082208448,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.228700758076806,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "てくれます。清らかな空気から",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.262060253972337,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.22592367706506677,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "純粋な水、肥沃な土壌から多様",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.28099964712258946,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.228700758076806,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "な生物まで、環境",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.29993904027284196,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.13003271954091566,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を保護し大切",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.29993904027284196,
      "left": 0.515659990278872,
      "width": 0.09801462038480707,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "にすることは、私たちの世代の",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3188784334230945,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.228700758076806,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "責任であり、未来の子孫が地球",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3378178265733471,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.228700758076806,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "の素晴らしさ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.35675721972359953,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.09801462038480711,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "を享受し続けるた",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.35675721972359953,
      "left": 0.48364189112276346,
      "width": 0.13019607835763847,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "めの鍵となります。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3756966128738521,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.14538835272462694,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "効果的なコ",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.40694661157176876,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.08167885317330739,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "ミュニケーションは",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.40694661157176876,
      "left": 0.4673061239112635,
      "width": 0.14702192201930678,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "異なる文",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4258860047220212,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.06534308596180759,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "化",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4258860047220212,
      "left": 0.4509703566997637,
      "width": 0.016335784327308006,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "、民族、国家の間に",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4258860047220212,
      "left": 0.4673061239112635,
      "width": 0.14702192201930678,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "理解と協力の重要な橋を架けま",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.44482539787227376,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.228700758076806,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "す。言語は人類の最も偉大な発",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4637647910225263,
      "left": 0.3856272878537643,
      "width": 0.22706718878212628,
      "height": 0.012623105439946337
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
